headline: Should You Buy Kinder Morgan Stock After Its Epic 50%+ Rally?
summary: Kinder Morgan (NYSE: KMI) had been in a rut for the past several years.  The natural gas pipeline giant's earnings barely budged as contract expirations offset the benefit of expansion projects.  Kinder Morgan's stock has skyrocketed, surging more than 50% so far this year, adding about $10 to the share price.
